umn;line-height:1}.mc-app__badge-sub{font-size:.5625rem;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;opacity:.7;margin-bottom:2px}.mc-app__badge-name{font-size:.9375rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.01em}@media(max-width:540px){.mc-app{padding:40px 20px}.mc-app__badges{flex-direction:column;align-items:center}.mc-app__badge{width:100%;max-width:240px;justify-content:center}}</style><div class=\"mc-app\"><div class=\"mc-app__inner\"><div class=\"mc-app__rule\"></div><p class=\"mc-app__eyebrow\">The App</p><h2 class=\"mc-app__heading\">All your body data,<br>in one place.</h2><p class=\"mc-app__sub\">Free forever. No subscription.</p><p class=\"mc-app__body\">Sync your N°01 Smart Ring with the QRing app. See your sleep, heart rate, recovery score, blood oxygen, and daily steps — all in one clean view.</p><div class=\"mc-app__steps\"><div class=\"mc-app__step\"><span class=\"mc-app__step-num\">1</span><p class=\"mc-app__step-text\"><strong>Download QRing</strong> — free on the App Store or Google Play.</p></div><div class=\"mc-app__step\"><span class=\"mc-app__step-num\">2</span><p class=\"mc-app__step-text\"><strong>Turn on Bluetooth</strong> on your phone and power on the ring.</p></div><div class=\"mc-app__step\"><span class=\"mc-app__step-num\">3</span><p class=\"mc-app__step-text\"><strong>Tap 'Add Device'</strong> in the app — the ring pairs in under 30 seconds.</p></div><div class=\"mc-app__step\"><span class=\"mc-app__step-num\">4</span><p class=\"mc-app__step-text\"><strong>Wear it to sleep</strong> — your data syncs by morning.</p></div></div><div class=\"mc-app__badges\"><a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/nz/app/qring/id6473672621\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"mc-app__badge\"><svg class=\"mc-app__badge-icon\" width=\"22\" height=\"26\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 26\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M18.05 13.77c-.03-3.2 2.62-4.75 2.74-4.82-1.5-2.19-3.82-2.49-4.64-2.52-1.97-.2-3.86 1.17-4.86 1.17-1.01 0-2.57-1.14-4.23-1.11C4.9 6.52 